1 (2) Pay any fee or charge related to the installation or use of
2 the plug-in solar power system.
3 (3) Install any additional controls or equipment, beyond what
4 is integrated into the electrical system of the customer's
5 building, in connection with the installation or use of the
6 plug-in solar power system.
7 Sec. 8. An electricity supplier is not liable for any injury or
8 damages caused by a customer's installation or use of a plug-in
9 solar power system.
